{
  "stem": "1354.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I thought that he-- oh, he always passed by.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He said, [GERMAN] you know, in-- in German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He never touched nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I never heard or saw for him to be, you know, cruel, or-- or-- And-- and I thought that he never pays attention to me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But after the war, we lived in Regensburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was coming out of the street car, and he was supposed to go to a street car.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When he saw me, he started to wave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he recognized me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he kissed me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he asked me how I am doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he recognized me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He talked to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But I kept-- it's a funny thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I still didn't-- it was too early.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I-- I didn't feel free with him, just to speak.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was still like the-- the-- I was still, like, afraid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He still was a-- he was a German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I guess so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- well, of course, I didn't know all the good things he did for other, you know, people, because the book what is written, I read stories about him, but I never knew that it-- that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And like I-- they were interviewing me here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And like I said, he was a human being.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First, he did it for himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the humanity kicked-- kicked in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he knew also, to the-- later on, that the Germans are losing the-- the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's why he was alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because in Brinnlitz-- we went later on to Brinnlitz-- our people got him out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Otherwise, the Russians-- because the Russians liberated us--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's-- that's-- that's the-- another story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- then it came out the-- well, we were in Plaszow-- came out the list.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
